âœ… HOW TO VISUALLY SEPARATE TITLE BAR & CONTENT (FlatLaf-Correct)

We will add ALL of these (safe & supported):

1. ğŸ¨ Different title bar background (gradient)


2. ğŸ“ Bottom divider line below title bar


3. ğŸŒ— Theme-aware colors


4. ğŸ§± No undecorated hacks


